'''急性腎小管壞死'''（{{lang-en|'''A'''cute '''t'''ubular '''n'''ecrosis}}，縮寫{{lang|en|'''ATN'''}}）為涉及[[腎|腎臟]][[腎單位|腎小管]][[上皮組織|上皮]][[细胞|细胞]][[壞死|壞死]]的醫學病症。ATN伴隨著[[急性腎損傷|急性腎損傷]]（acute kidney injury，AKI），並且是AKI的最常見的病因之一<ref name="Acute Tubular Necrosis ATN">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nephrologychannel.com/atn/index.shtml |title=Acute Tubular Necrosis (ATN) |accessdate=2008-09-23 |year=2008 |work=Nephrology Channel |publisher=HealthCommunities.com |archive-date=2018-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180722085321/http://www.nephrologychannel.com/atn/index.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。ATN常見的病因包括[[低血壓|低血壓]]，及使用{{le|中毒性腎損害|nephrotoxic|腎毒性}}藥物<ref name="Acute Tubular Necrosis ATN"/>。[[尿液分析|尿液分析]]時在尿中發現上皮細胞的「棕色渾濁[[管型_(尿液)|管型尿液]]」是ATN的{{le|特異病徵性|pathognomonic}}<ref name="Goldman, L 2004 705">{{Cite book|author=Goldman, Lee; Cecil, Russell L. |title=Cecil medicine |publisher=Saunders Elsevier |location=Philadelphia, PA |year=2008 |page=705 |isbn=0-8089-2377-3 |oclc=191854838}}</ref>。ATN的治療依靠的是沉澱ATN（比如[[靜脈注射|水化]]及停止使用違規藥物）的因素進行。由於腎小管的上皮細胞會不斷自行更替，如果病因在發現及治療後、則ATN的整體預後是相當不錯的，且可能在7到21天左右康復<ref name="Acute Tubular Necrosis ATN"/>。

==分類==
ATN可以分類為[[毒性|中毒性]]（Toxic）及[[缺血|缺血性]]（Ischemia）兩種。當管狀細胞暴露於有毒物質（{{le|中毒性腎損害|nephrotoxic|腎毒性}}ATN）時，則會發生中毒性ATN。當腎小管細胞沒有得到足夠的氧氣時，則會發生缺血性ATN；腎小管細胞對於環境相當敏感且易受感染，因為他們有相當旺盛的[[代謝|代謝]]作用<ref name=Goldman2008>{{Cite book|author=Goldman, Lee; Cecil, Russell L. |title=Cecil medicine |publisher=Saunders Elsevier |location=Philadelphia, PA |year=2008 |page= |isbn=0-8089-2377-3 |oclc=191854838}}{{Page needed|date=September 2010}}</ref>。

==診斷==
{{seealso|腎功能|腎生理學}}

急性腎小管壞死被歸為急性腎損傷的腎因性病因。診斷是由{{le|鈉排泄分數|fractional excretion of sodium}}（FENA）>3％，及[[尿液分析|尿液分析]]呈「泥濘石膏」狀（一種[[管型_(尿液)|尿液管型]]）來進行判定。組織病理學上，通常有{{le|腎小管破裂|tubulorrhexis}}，即位於腎小管上皮襯裡的壞死、與局灶性破裂或[[腎小球基底膜|基底膜]]的損失。<ref>[http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/tubulorrhexis TheFreeDictionary > tubulorrhexis] {{Wayback|url=http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/tubulorrhexis |date=20210310045610 }} Citing: The American Heritage Medical Dictionary 2007</ref>近端小管細胞可以擺脫可變的生存能力且不會是純粹的壞死。<ref>{{Cite journal |author=Glynne PA, Picot J, Evans TJ |title=Coexpressed nitric oxide synthase and apical beta(1) integrins influence tubule cell adhesion after cytokine-induced injury |journal=Journal of the American Society of Nephrology |volume=12 |issue=11 |pages=2370–83 |date=November 2001 |pmid=11675413 |url=http://jasn.asnjournals.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=11675413 |access-date=2014-12-13 |archive-date=2022-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516204736/https://jasn.asnjournals.org/content/12/11/2370.long }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author=Glynne PA, Evans TJ |title=Inflammatory cytokines induce apoptotic and necrotic cell shedding from human proximal tubular epithelial cell monolayers |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_kidney-international_1999-06_55_6/page/2573 |journal=Kidney International |volume=55 |issue=6 |pages=2573–97 |date=June 1999 |pmid=10354308 |doi=10.1046/j.1523-1755.2002.t01-1-00456.x}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author=Racusen LC |title=Epithelial cell shedding in acute renal injury |journal=Clinical and Experimental Pharmacology & Physiology |volume=25 |issue=3–4 |pages=273–5 |year=1998 |pmid=9590582 |doi=10.1111/j.1440-1681.1998.t01-3-.x}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|author=Solez K, Racusen LC, Marcussen N, ''et al.'' |title=Morphology of ischemic acute kidney injury, normal function, and cyclosporine toxicity in cyclosporine-treated renal allograft recipients |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_kidney-international_1993-05_43_5/page/